text={
[1]={
ja={
{
"町に、異変が起きていた。",
},
},
en={
{
"It was a major incident.",
},
},
},
[2]={
ja={
{
"いや、これは。",
},
},
en={
{
"No, scratch that.",
},
},
},
[3]={
ja={
{
"異変ではなく、転機だった。",
},
},
en={
{
"This wasn't an incident, but a turning point.",
},
},
},
[4]={
ja={
{
"まだ夕焼けには早い時間。",
},
},
en={
{
"The sun had yet to sink beyond the horizon.",
},
},
},
[5]={
ja={
{
"夕方に差しかかろうとする頃のこと。",
},
},
en={
{
"It was just starting to lower.",
},
},
},
[6]={
ja={
{
"山代修司は、天を仰ぎ見た。",
},
},
en={
{
"Yamashiro Shuuji looked up towards the heavens.",
},
},
},
[7]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00451",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「なんだ……これは……？」",
},
},
en={
{
"「What... the hell...?」",
},
},
},
[8]={
ja={
{
"町の空に、光の泡が立ち昇っている。",
},
},
en={
{
"Bubbles of light were rising up over the townscape.",
},
},
},
[9]={
ja={
{
"風に舞う、自由なシャボン玉のようにして。",
},
},
en={
{
"Freely riding the wind like soap bubbles.",
},
},
},
[10]={
ja={
{
"光り輝きながら空一面に広がるそれは、まるでオーロラのようだった。",
},
},
en={
{
"They spread and lit up the sky like an aurora.",
},
},
},
[11]={
ja={
{
"オーロラとは、地上に夜明けをもたらす意味を持つ……。",
},
},
en={
{
"A phenomenon that means 'dawn' in Latin...",
},
},
},
[12]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00452",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「これは……まさか……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Are you serious...?」",
},
},
},
[13]={
ja={
{
"こんなにもたくさんの魂人が、今まさに、還っている……。",
},
},
en={
{
"He could see that countless tamabito were returning...",
},
},
},
[14]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00453",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「誰かが還してるんじゃねえ……。魂人が、自ら還ってるのか……？」",
},
},
en={
{
"「They aren't bein' sent back... They're returnin' of their own volition...?」",
},
},
},
[15]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00454",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「この町……彩香町の魂人、全員が一緒に……？」",
},
},
en={
{
"「The tamabito of Saika... all at once...?」",
},
},
},
[16]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00455",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「ありえねえ……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「No fuckin' way...」",
},
},
},
[17]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00456",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「どうすれば、こんなことができるんだ……？」",
},
},
en={
{
"「How's this even possible...?」",
},
},
},
[18]={
ja={
{
"山代は極光が広がる天を見上げながら、呆然としたあと。",
},
},
en={
{
"Yamashiro stared in bafflement at the expanding torrent of light in the sky.",
},
},
},
[19]={
ja={
{
"笑った。",
},
},
en={
{
"And laughed.",
},
},
},
[20]={
ja={
{
"もはや、この気持ちを吐き出すには、笑うしかなかった。",
},
},
en={
{
"There was no other way to express what he was feeling.",
},
},
},
[21]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00457",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「ハハッ……ちくしょう」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Haha... screw me.」",
},
},
},
[22]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00458",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「やられたぜ、まったく」",
},
},
en={
{
"「You got us good.」",
},
},
},
[23]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00459",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「これじゃあ、送り人の立つ瀬がねえ」",
},
},
en={
{
"「So much for us okuribito.」",
},
},
},
[24]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_yms_00460",ch="man"},
},
name={name="山代",ja="山代",en="Yamashiro"},
ja={
{
"「俺の立つ瀬がねえよ……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「There's no stage for me to stand on...」",
},
},
},
},
label={
},
}
